description: This beautiful emission-free Bangkok taxi (or Tuk Tuk) is bringing the best brewed teas to ever flow, straight through the streets of Buffalo. You’ll most likely find this three-wheeled mobile machine to be quite keen, as it helps our planet to stay green with its limited carbon footprint. And with their commitment to supply such a delightful selection of the tastiest teas of the utmost quality, Tuk Tea is the fully noble food truck experience we all need.
name: Tuk Tea Company
